## Resolve OAI identifier

OAIs are unique identifiers used by repositories. As opposed to DOIs, they are minted in a distributed way and cost-free. Our service allows you to resolve an OAI in the same way as you would resolve a DOI.

[Resolve](http://oai.core.ac.uk)
